                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9942" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1501</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1455 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“固”事新篇：彩乐股份税务风险管理的合规花开</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New Chapter of &quot;Fixed Assets&quot; Stories: The Blossoming of Compliance in CaiLe Shares&#39; Tax Risk Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张睿，路明，许秋菊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">彩乐科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">税务风险管理；固定资产涉税处理；内部控制；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tax risk management, Tax related treatment of fixed assets, Internal control</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业税务风险管理对于确保企业的合法合规经营、提升经济效率至关重要。化工行业作为重资产行业的典型，以固定资产为代表的长期投资决策不仅对经营业绩影响重大，且涉税场景的复杂性更是对企业税务管理提出了更高要求。在精细化工行业竞争加剧的背景下，彩乐未来通过企业并购实现规模扩张，其子公司彩乐股份承接母公司亿元在建工程资产后，因历史遗留问题与内部控制失效，导致无票资产折旧税前扣除、关联方借款利息处理不当和设备折旧年限估计不准确等问题集中爆发，陷入税务风险泥潭。面对困局，企业采取了一系列措施，通过建立税务风险清单、责任分工清单和整改落实清单，构建起税务风险识别、评估、应对、控制和监管的管理体系，有效降低了税务风险，并主动申报享受了税收优惠。本案例以彩乐股份的固定资产涉税处理为递进脉络，深入剖析了企业税务风险管理从“被动响应”到“系统防范”的发展过程，旨在培养学生的税务风险管理意识，同时也为其他企业的经营管理提供一定的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Enterprise tax risk management is of great significance for ensuring the legal and compliant operation of enterprises and improving economic efficiency. As a typical representative of heavy asset industry, the chemical industry&#39;s long term investment decisions represented by fixed assets not only have a significant impact on operating performance, but also the complexity of tax related scenarios puts forward higher requirements for enterprise tax management. Against the backdrop of intensified competition in the fine chemical industry, CaiLe Future realizes scale expansion through enterprise mergers and acquisitions. After its subsidiary CaiLe Co., Ltd. undertakes hundreds of millions of yuan of construction-in-progress assets from the parent company, due to historical legacy issues and internal control failures, problems such as the pre-tax deduction of depreciation of non-invoiced assets, improper handling of interest on related - party loans, and inaccurate estimation of the depreciation period of equipment have broken out intensively, plunging it into a quagmire of tax risks. Facing the predicament, the enterprise has taken a series of measures. By establishing a tax risk list, a responsibility division list and a rectification and implementation list, it has built a management system for tax risk identification, assessment, response, control and supervision, effectively reducing tax risks and taking the initiative to declare and enjoy tax incentives. Taking the tax related treatment of fixed assets of CaiLe Co., Ltd. as a progressive context, this case deeply analyzes the development process of enterprise tax risk management from &quot;passive response&quot; to &quot;systematic prevention&quot;, aiming to cultivate students&#39; awareness of tax risk management and provide some reference for the operation and management of other enterprises at the same time.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业税务风险管理》、《内部控制》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">税务风险的分类；税收风险管理体系；固定资产涉税处理；税收法律法规的适用判断。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
